chanters on during peak time.  (/who all 60 enchanter gnome/dark/high/etc can give you an idea)  But it would be a safe bet for me to say more warlocks were epicced then enchanters, even though there are less of us.</P><P>Why?</P><P>Our epic is easy.</P><P><img src="http://www.users.qwest.net/~morbid909/SIG4.jpg" border=0><BR> <br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=107355" target="_blank">Those who have turned away, shall be turned upon.</a>  <img src=icon_smile_evil.gif border=0 align=middle></font></td>
